# Lab 009 - Attach Public IP to Azure VM

## Method
Azure CLI

## Objective
Attach an existing Public IP address to an existing Azure Virtual Machine by updating its Network Interface Card (NIC).

## Azure Services
- Azure Virtual Machine
- Network Interface (NIC)
- Public IP
- Resource Group

## Steps
1. List available NICs.
2. Identify the correct Resource Group.
3. List available Public IP addresses.
4. Find the NIC IP configuration.
5. Attach the Public IP.
6. Verify the configuration.

